{
  "design_notes": "The medium chart mirrors the progression of the track's energy. Intro features quiet sparse taps with no sudden jumps. The buildup introduces subtle eighth-note groupings and a simple hold. The main drop starting at Bar 16 kicks up the density with rhythmic eighth-note streams and accents mapped to jumps. We integrated the natural holds of the song to hit a comfortable 7% hold share. The density decays elegantly down to quarter notes and finally wraps up with quiet, sparse outro notes to prevent any dead pauses.",
